    "(C) Labeling using keyphrase extractionTo construct an accurate database, we required a labeled dataset.",
    "However, labeling 1769 web pages manually would have been prohibitively labor-intensive.",
    "To simplify the process, we utilized an NLP tool named Keyphrase Extraction.",
    "The purpose is to extract a few phrases that can help readers comprehend the content of a text quickly.",
    "Keyphrases are made up of multiple words, unlike keywords, which consist of single words."
